🔹 6. Exercises for Deep Research (DR‑X)

DR‑X1: Pattern Extraction

Collect 5 examples of similar institutional behavior and identify the common thread.

DR‑X2: Incentive Mapping

List the incentives of each actor in a system and predict how they shape decisions.

DR‑X3: Visibility Threshold Analysis

Identify what level of documentation triggers institutional engagement.

DR‑X4: Posture Reconstruction

Rebuild a timeline from artifacts to understand how posture changed over time.

DR‑X5: Gatekeeper Behavior Audit

Analyze how gatekeepers filter, accept, or reject cases.

These exercises train the learner to see what most people miss.

